  <metadata>
    <name>Tour 24: Zabergäu &amp; Heuchelberg</name>
    <desc>A shorter, relaxed tour through the gentle wine hills of the Zabergäu and Heuchelberg—discover the UNESCO-listed Maulbronn Monastery and charming wine villages without breaking a sweat.</desc>
    <author>
      <name>Hockenheim Motorcycle Tours</name>
    </author>
  </metadata>
